Canonical website:
  http://mailnotify.nongnu.org/

Canonical download:
  http://savannah.nongnu.org/download/mailnotify/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack mail-notification-5.4-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./mail-notification-5.4-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/mail-notification-5.4-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/mail-notification-5.4-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

